	<p>I've thought about making a toon on one of them PvP servers, a Shaman of course, but I want grind out Gundaam some more.  <br />
What are those servers really like?  I imagine it's something like a cross between reruns of Oz and being nestled in the belly of the all-powerful Sarlacc, where you can find a new definition of pain and suffering, as you are slowly digested over a thousand years.</p>
	
	
	
