	<!-- message -->
	<p>People seem to think that just because we fight eachother, we have no friends on our server.<br />
<br />
Let me put it like this:<br />
<br />
We have to depend and cherish out friends even more, because without them, life on the Zeks would be truly hard and meaningless.<br />
<br />
The focus is on "we against them", where "we" is more important than them. We have many enemies, who we fight at different times, but we have only a few friends, who we stick together with always.<br />
<br />
We fight hard but we stick together harder. <img src="images/smilies/smile.gif" border="0" alt="" title="smile" smilieid="1" /><br />
<br />
Besides, the servers have different categories of mentality. I like to think of Sullon like a gang-war and Vallon/Tallon like a fist-boxing fight.</p>
	
	
	
