	<p>Everyone's saying not to play on Sullon, but howler sure is selling it well.  I mean, he doesn't make it sound pretty, but it sounds like it's zomething different.  I mean, it looks like Sullon is the worst of the worst.  I kinda get the impression that, "if you can make it on Sullon, you can make it anywhere."  I mean, I don't intend to stop playing my 53 shaman on Sol Ro, I'd just like to have another server to go to, and one with a different sort of flavor.  I just don't know about being a shaman though.  Like I said before, I guess I would choose a Shaman cause that's what I know, and then there's the defense aspect with gate, sow, and healing.  I bet it'll be a pain in the ass though.  There's a lot of good info in this thread.  I won't be able to play much this weekend, but I'm going to try to try to make a guy on one of these PVP servers this weekend.  Still going to do some research till then on which server to start on, and what kind of a toon to create.<br />
<br />
And for the people suggesting I might want to try a different game for PVP.  I guess I appreciate the thought, but my PC is for EQ, porn, checking sports scores, and porn.  The next game I will buy will be the new Madden for Xbox or PS2, I haven't decided.  I don't really want another game for my PC right now.  But thanks anyway.</p>
	
	
	
